-Mhm.

302
00:18:12.229 --> 00:18:13.229
Thank you.

303
00:18:14.645 --> 00:18:16.578
You made me look
stupid in front of her.

304
00:18:17.786 --> 00:18:19.408
[coughing fit]

305
00:18:29.384 --> 00:18:30.384
[sighs]

306
00:18:34.527 --> 00:18:35.631
