You're probably just dehydrated.
Why don't you try drinking some water?

452
00:28:09.170 --> 00:28:10.205
My ears hurt.

453
00:28:10.240 --> 00:28:11.240
Really bad.

454
00:28:14.175 --> 00:28:15.486
You're really warm.

455
00:28:17.143 --> 00:28:18.766
[call button chimes]

456
