I'm sorry to bother you. but do you
happen to have any Tylenol or Advil?

457
00:28:22.390 --> 00:28:23.805
Sure.

458
00:28:25.358 --> 00:28:27.198
We just have a few questions for
you. Chloe. Just have a seat right here.

459
00:28:27.222 --> 00:28:28.741
Let Mommy go first. okay?

460
00:28:33.125 --> 00:28:35.472
Emma here tells me
you're not feeling well.

461
